36:59.754 --> 37:00.934
Wait...

37:00.935 --> 37:03.914
It's the only photo of the
three of us together.

37:03.915 --> 37:05.834
It's just, you know,

37:05.835 --> 37:09.834
I-I had it framed for you.

37:09.835 --> 37:13.934
If something happens to me,
